parameters:
"This is a completely unfamiliar building. It
doesn't seem like a mansion from this country."\n<Yukine>\F[8]

"Since it's also my first time seeing this
building, let's be careful as we move forward."\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[24]
"Onee-san, I'm sorry for causing you trouble."\n<Shuo>\F[8]\AA[FF]\FF[23]

"No, not at all. I don't think it's a bother in
the slightest."\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[23]

"It's hard to see, but... it's sparkling and
pretty, isn't it?"\n<Shuo>\F[1]\AA[FF]\FF[40]

"That's right... Shaku, you hold onto this until
we find where it can be used."\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[40]

"Little fox, you need not concern yourself with
the use of the key."\n<???>\F[1]\AA[FF]\FF[25]\AA[N]

"How dare you call my name so casually, insolent
little fox... Stand back!"\n<Sakari Tsuki>\FF[33]

"Hmm... Even a little fox is at the end of the
gods' table. I thought I had crushed that
incarnate heart of yours..."\n<Sakari Tsuki>\FF[35]

"Useless creatures who let it escape time and
again. Those who cannot even hunt a fox are of no
use to me."\n<Sakari Tsuki>\FF[37]
"Just by lightly touching that evil spirit..."\n<Yukine>\F[15]

"Now, Shaku. It's about time you returned to my
side."\n<Sakka Tsuki>\FF[38]

"That should be enough... You are my shrine
maiden. Stop frolicking with little foxes."\n<Sakari Tsuki>\FF[38]

"What dissatisfies you, Shaku... You can spend
eternity in this world. Without feeling sadness,
pain, or anxiety, why do you run? Do you intend to
betray me?"\n<Sakka Tsuki>\FF[31]

"Come back, Shaku. You who were abandoned are most
fitting by my side."\n<Sakka Tsuki>\FF[38]

"*cough*... To bind Shaku in such a cold darkness,
to take away all her senses so she can't feel
anything..."\n<Yukine>\F[19]\AA[F]\FF[22]

"Do you know how lonely Shaku has been! Cursing
many people, killing plenty with curses, leaving
Shaku all alone in the world--You don't care about
Shaku at all."\n<Yukine>\F[19]\AA[F]\FF[23]

"You insolent creature... How dare a mere fox mock
me."\n<Sakka Tsuki>\FF[37]

"*gasp*, such a terrible curse. My throat, my skin
is burning."\n<Yukine>\F[15]\AA[F]\FF[26]

"Enough... I shall personally punish you. Once I
flay your skin, gouge out your eyes, and drag out
your entrails, perhaps Shaku's heart will change."\n<Sakka Tsuki>\FF[32]

"God... please stop... don't do horrible things to
Onee-san."\n<Shuo>\F[15]\AA[FF]\FF[26]

"Ah, poor Shaku. I will save you from the warmth
soon. Just wait a little."\n<Sakka Tsuki>\FF[32]

(It seems like there's nothing here, just a layer
of dust.)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here...)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here.)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here...)
(I wonder if there's anything useful here...)
(I wonder if this key will fit...)
(Is there anything else that might be useful?)
(It seems like there's nothing inside this)
(There's a picture of flowers on display.)
(...Looking at it makes my heart race.)

"Onee-san... my body feels warm... I feel kind of
strange."\n<Shuo>\FF[23]

"Me too... Let's rest here for a bit, Saku...
*pant* *pant*"\n<Yukine>\F[9]\AA[F]\FF[23]
Let's take a look at the scene

(There's a picture of a beautiful woman on
display.)
(I wonder if this key will fit...)
(Thank goodness, it looks like it fits)
